{"version":1,"entries":{"tv_309604_keywords":{"at":1772689421405,"data":{"id":309604,"results":[{"name":"1990s","id":210608}]}},"person_3028903_translations":{"at":1772689426469,"data":{"id":3028903,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Pond Naravit Lertratkosum is an actor under GMMTV. He is currently studying Biomedical Engineering in the Faculty of Engineering at King Mongkut's Institute of Technology Ladkrabang.\n\nIn 2020, Pond was a winner of the third Go On Girl & Guy Star Search by Clean & Clear after which he was signed under GMMTV\n\nDuring his university life, Pond was crowned the hottest guy of the Faculty of Engineering.\n\nPond is the founder of the clothing brand Apollo.","name":"Naravit Lertratkosum","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ณราวิชญ์ เลิศรัตน์โกมุสภ์","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"纳拉维特·勒拉格苏（ณราราวิชญ์ เลิศรัตน์โกสุมภ์，Naravit Lertratkosum），艺名Pond（ปอนด์），2001年2月1日出生于泰国，泰国男演员，毕业于泰国先皇理工大学，现为GMMTV旗下艺人 。2020年签约GMMTV后，客串出演校园剧《特长生2》正式出道。2021年主演同志爱情剧《鱼你相医》受到关注 。2022年获Kazz Awards年度上升之星，同年主演爱情剧《绝不放手》并在剧中饰演Palm 。2023年参演《午夜系列之脏脏洗衣店》《我们的天空 II》及《孤独社畜》等多部剧集 。2024年主演校园爱情剧《我们彼此相爱》饰演Phum。2025年推出《闰日夺魂》《清醒点,泰尔先生》等新作。","name":"纳拉维特·勒拉格苏","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"納拉維特·勒拉格蘇（ณราราวิชญ์ เลิศรัตน์โกสุมภ์，納爾瓦夫·勒特拉特桑），藝名 Pond（ปอนด์），2001 年 2 月 1 日出生於泰國，泰國男演員，畢業於泰國先皇理工大學，現為 GMMTV 旗下藝人 。2020 年簽約 GMMTV 後，客串出演校園劇《特長生 2》正式出道。2021 年主演同志愛情劇《魚你相醫》受到關注 。2022 年獲 Kazz Awards 年度上升之星，同年主演愛情劇《絕不放手》並在劇中飾演 Palm 。2023 年參演《午夜系列之髒髒洗衣店》《我們的天空 II》及《孤獨社畜》等多部劇集 。2024 年主演校園愛情劇《我們彼此相愛》飾演 Phum。2025 年推出《閏日奪魂》《清醒點, 泰爾先生》等新作。","name":"納爾瓦夫·勒特拉特桑","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ナラウィット・ルートラコム","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Naravit Lertratkosum, conhecido como Pond, é um ator e cantor tailandês agenciado pela GMMTV. Ele ingressou na agência após vencer a terceira edição do concurso \"Go On Girl & Guy Star Search\" em 2020. Na vida acadêmica, Pond estuda na Faculdade de Engenharia do King Mongkut's Institute of Technology Ladkrabang (KMITL); ele iniciou em Engenharia Biomédica, mas migrou para Gestão de Engenharia e Empreendedorismo para conciliar os estudos com sua agenda profissional.\n\nPond alcançou o estrelato global ao protagonizar a série \"Fish Upon the Sky\" (2021), onde iniciou sua parceria de sucesso com Phuwin Tangsakyuen. Em 2024, expandiu sua carreira musical ao estrear no grupo de performance JASP.ER, sob o selo Riser Music, com o single \"Sadistic\". Além de estrelar produções como \"Never Let Me Go\" e a aguardada \"Me And Thee\" (2025), Pond é o fundador da marca de roupas Apollo.","name":"Pond Naravit Lertratkosum","primary":false}}]}},"person_2876433_translations":{"at":1772689432671,"data":{"id":2876433,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"郑小毛，从事舞台银幕演艺四十余年，现任东莞市文联朗诵家协会、曲艺家协会理事。东莞市微电影协会演艺工作委员会指导老师，主要作品有《双手洪拳》。","name":"郑小毛","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zheng Xiaomao","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"鄭小毛","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"鄭小毛，從事舞台銀幕演藝四十餘年，現任東莞市文聯朗誦家協會、曲藝家協會理事。東莞市微電影協會演藝工作委員會指導老師，主要作品有《雙手洪拳》。","name":"鄭小毛","primary":false}}]}},"person_4807833_translation